    - full name
    - short name / code
    - capacity
    - type (theory, lab, computer lab, general classroom)

- teacher
    [X] full name
    [X] seniority level
    [X] rank
    [X] maximum teaching load per day/week
    [] preferred time slots

- courses
    - title and short code
    - credit hours
    - offered by which department
    - assigned to which teacher
    - type (theory, lab, computer lab)
    - duration (1, 2 or 3)

- 8 AM to 5 PM : 1 hour, 2 hours and 3 hours

