    - name / code
    - department
    - number of students
    - assignmend home classroom (must)

- sub-section for labs

- conflicts
    - two sec in same classroom at same time
    - teacher assigned to multiple classes at same time
    - classroom capacity

- senior teacher preferred time

- separate timetable
    - each section
    - each teacher
    - each classroom
    - each course

